text: niyata vaśayenma api mūsāṭa pæhædili prātihāryayan navayak dī ættemu. (nabiyē! mē gæna) oba isrāyīla paramparāvē daruvangen vimasā (dæna ganu mænava!) (mūsā) ovun veta pæmiṇi viṭa, firavun ohuṭa “ō mūsā! niyata vaśayenma oba sūniyamen manasa vikṛti vūveku yayi mā obava gaṇan gannemi” yayi kīvēya
